      "text": [
        " \"مَا هُوَ\" فَقُلْتُ اَلْأَحْمَقُ اَلذَّاهِبُ اَلْعَقْلِ فَقَالَ \"نَعَمْ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4771 - Ḥammad ibn ʿIsa narrated from Shuʿayb, from Abu Baṣir, from Abu Abdullah (as), that Imam (as) who was asked about the validity of a divorce issued by a mentally impaired person (ma'tooh).\nImam (as) responded: \"What do you mean by that?\"\nI said: \"The foolish one who lacks sound reasoning.\"\nImam (as) replied: \"Yes, it is valid.\""
        ]
      }
    },
